Stage 1
Collect users weight in kilograms 
Collect height in meters
Calculate users BMI

Stage 2
Prompt user to enter weight
Collect weight from user
Store weight of user as weightinkilograms
Prompt user to enter height
Collect weight from user
Store weight of user as heightinmeters
Calculate BMI using (weightinkilograms)/(heightinmeters * heightinmeters)
Store calculation in bmi
Display the result of calculation